          <tbody class="text-ink">
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted">BFS 分层</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">记录队列长度，按层出队</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">层序遍历、右视图、最短路</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted">DFS + 深度</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">传递 depth，按需记录首访</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">右视图、路径总和、最大深度</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted">拓扑排序（Kahn）</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">入度 0 入队，出队减后继入度</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">课程表、任务调度</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted">DFS 拓扑</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">后序逆序即拓扑序</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">课程表、拓扑排序</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted">访问标记</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">图需 vis[]，注意多连通分量</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">连通分量、岛屿数量</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
